## Description
Adds :active pseudo-class states for better touch feedback on mobile.

## Problem
- No visual feedback when button is pressed on touch
- Users unsure if tap registered
- Missing tactile response on mobile
- Poor mobile interaction feel

## Solution
- Add active:bg-* states to all button variants
- Darker shade when pressed (80% opacity)
- Applies to all interactive elements
- Better touch feedback

## Impact
- Clear visual feedback on tap
- Better mobile UX
- Feels more responsive
- Meets WCAG interaction guidelines

## Testing
- Tap buttons on touch device
- Verify darker shade appears
- Test all button variants
- Check doesn't interfere with hover states
